Titulo: The Evaluation of Ca Doped GDC Electrolyte Thin Film for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells by Electron Beam Deposition

Sentencas: The GDC thin films were deposited on porous Ni-GDC anode pellet.
Titulo: The Evaluation of Ca Doped GDC Electrolyte Thin Film for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells by Electron Beam Deposition

Sentencas: Operating technical parameters that influence thin film microstructure and crystallite size were studied.

Sentencas: It was found that electron gun power (changed in the range of 0.60 to 1.05 kW) has the influence on the crystallite size of GDC thin films and decreased linearly increasing electron beam gun power.
